### Transferring mp4 file to mpeg
```
for file in *.mp4; do ffmpeg -i "$file" -c:v mpeg2video -qscale:v 2 -an "${file%.mp4}.mpeg"; done
```

### Deploying on raspberry pi needs to change the following:
```
// Use the Raspberry Pi's hardware decoder for HEVC (H.265)
codec = avcodec_find_decoder_by_name("h265_v4l2m2m");
```